OL,3,CMarket trader 'felt untouchable' as he
OL,4,Cabused schoolgirls, court hears
OL,6,FA market trader who groomed and raped
OL,7,Ftwo schoolgirls in Rochdale believed
OL,8,Fhe was "untouchable", a court has
OL,9,Fheard.
OL,11,FMohammed Zahid, 65, was convicted
OL,12,Fearlier this year alongside six other
OL,13,Fmen for a series of historical sexual
OL,14,Foffences committed between 2001 and
OL,15,F2006.
OL,17,FHe is due to be sentenced on Wednesday
OL,18,F1 October at Manchester Minshull
OL,19,FStreet Crown Court.
