OL,3,CMarket trader 'felt untouchable' as he
OL,4,Cabused schoolgirls, court hears
OL,6,FZahid, known locally as "Boss Man",
OL,7,Fran a lingerie stall at Rochdale
OL,8,FIndoor Market. Prosecutors said he
OL,9,Fused it as a base to target vulnerable
OL,10,Fgirls, offering free underwear, food,
OL,11,Falcohol and money in exchange for
OL,12,Fsexual access to them and his
OL,13,Fassociates.
OL,15,FOne of the victims, referred to as
OL,16,FGirl B, was living in a children's
OL,17,Fhome at the time.
OL,19,FProsecutor Rossano Scamardella KC told
OL,20,Fthe court that Zahid's behaviour
OL,21,Fbecame increasingly brazen.
