OL,3,CMarket trader 'felt untouchable' as he
OL,4,Cabused schoolgirls, court hears
OL,6,F"He would ring the care home and go
OL,7,Fthere to pick her up and drop her
OL,8,Foff," he said. "By the end of the
OL,9,Fabuse he felt almost untouchable."
OL,11,FThe court heard that Girl B had
OL,12,Freported the abuse to carers and
OL,13,Fsocial services, but no action was
OL,14,Ftaken. Jurors were told she had been
OL,15,Flabelled as a "prostitute" by Rochdale
OL,16,Fsocial services from the age of just
OL,17,F10.
