OL,3,CMarket trader 'felt untouchable' as he
OL,4,Cabused schoolgirls, court hears
OL,6,FIt also emerged that two 16-year-olds
OL,7,Fmade written complaints to the market
OL,8,Fmanagement at the time, alleging that
OL,9,FZahid gave them discounted items and
OL,10,Fmade sexual comments but no further
OL,11,Faction followed.
OL,13,FZahid was previously jailed for five
OL,14,Fyears in 2016 for sexually abusing a
OL,15,F14-year-old girl he met at the same
OL,16,Fmarket stall.
