OL,3,CMarket trader 'felt untouchable' as he
OL,4,Cabused schoolgirls, court hears
OL,6,FHis barrister, Lisa Wilding KC, said
OL,7,Fhe continues to deny the current
OL,8,Foffences, but acknowledged he now
OL,9,Ffaces the prospect of spending the
OL,10,Frest of his life in prison.
OL,12,F"I would ask you to pass a sentence
OL,13,Fthat perhaps allows him a glimmer of
OL,14,Fhope that at some stage he may be
OL,15,Freleased," she told the judge.
