OL,3,CMarket trader 'felt untouchable' as he
OL,4,Cabused schoolgirls, court hears
OL,6,FZahid, of Station Road, Crumpsall, was
OL,7,Ffound guilty of multiple counts of
OL,8,Frape, indecency with a child and
OL,9,Fprocuring a child for sex against two
OL,10,Fgirls, Girl A and Girl B, who did not
OL,11,Fknow each other.
OL,13,FThe barrister for another convicted
OL,14,Fman, Mustaq Ahmed, found guilty of
OL,15,Fraping Girl B, told the court he was
OL,16,F"sorry for what he's done".
OL,18,FThe court heard as a result he had
OL,19,Flost his income, and he can no longer
OL,20,Fsupport his family and a further 18
OL,21,Fpeople he helped in Pakistan.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/8
